---
// BLVSTACK wordmark — uses Λ (Greek capital Lambda, U+039B) as the stylized 'A'.
// It's a letter character so it inherits surrounding font weight/size cleanly.
// Screen readers + crawlers see "BLVSTACK" via the sr-only span (real text in DOM).
// The decorative span with Λ is aria-hidden so it's not double-read.
---
<span style="white-space: nowrap;"
  ><span class="sr-only">BLVSTACK</span><span aria-hidden="true">BLVSTΛCK</span></span>
